       <div id="viewlet-above-content-title"></div> 
       <h1 id="parent-fieldname-title" class="documentFirstHeading"> Department of Geology </h1> 
       <div id="viewlet-below-content-title"> 
       </div> 
       <div id="viewlet-above-content-body"> 
       </div> 
       <div id="content-core"> 
        <div id="parent-fieldname-text-01dbf24fa6968bda4de23fe30c08cb5f" class=""> 
         <p class="opening">According to students, Leicester is the best place in the UK to come and study for a geology degree.</p> 
         <p>The vibrant atmosphere reflects our commitment to the best teaching and support for students, combined with world class research published in leading international journals. Our research income for the past&nbsp;6 years exceeds £10M, and we have strong industrial research and teaching links across the environment, minerals and oil &amp; gas sectors.</p> 
         <table class="plain"> 
          <tbody> 
           <tr> 
            <td><a href="http://www2.le.ac.uk/departments/geology/ugcourses" class="internal-link" title="Undergraduate Courses"><img alt="Undergraduate Courses" class="image-inline" height="100" src="images/undergraduate.jpg" width="250"></a></td> 
            <td><a href="http://www2.le.ac.uk/departments/geology/pgstudy" class="internal-link" title="Postgraduate Study"><img alt="Postgraduate Study" class="image-inline" height="100" src="images/postgraduate.jpg" width="250"> </a></td> 
           </tr> 
           <tr> 
            <td><a href="http://www2.le.ac.uk/departments/geology/research" class="internal-link" title="Research"><img alt="Research" class="image-inline" height="100" src="images/deptresearch.jpg" width="250"></a></td> 
            <td><a href="http://www2.le.ac.uk/departments/geology/geoblog" class="internal-link" title="Why Choose Leicester"><img src="http://www2.le.ac.uk/departments/geology/images/buttons/geoblog" title="GeoBlog" alt="GeoBlog" class="image-inline" height="100" width="250"></a></td> 
           </tr> 
          </tbody> 
         </table> 
         <h3>Where are we in the National Subject League Tables?</h3> 
         <p>Geology at Leicester is consistently ranked as one of the top 10 departments in the UK:</p> 
         <ul> 
          <li>5th in the Times Good University Guide 2013</li> 
          <li>5th in the <a class="external-link" href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/education/table/2013/jun/04/university-guide-earth-marine-sciences">National Guardian University 2014</a> subject tables</li> 
          <li>8th in the <a class="external-link" href="http://www.thecompleteuniversityguide.co.uk/league-tables/rankings?s=Geology">Complete University Guide 2013</a> subject tables</li> 
          <li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.facebook.com/GeologyLeics/posts/868194046524870">National Student Survey 2014</a></li> 
          <li><a href="http://www2.le.ac.uk/departments/geology/ugcourses/national-student-survey-2011" class="internal-link" title="National Student Survey 2011">National Student Survey 2011</a></li> 
         </ul> 
        </div> 
       </div> 
